              <span class="highlight">mobilize women and men</span> as
              modern-day Esthers and Mordecais—calling nations to prayer,
              fasting, and spiritual awakening for the fulfillment of their
              prophetic destiny, and to secure a future for the next generation.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mission-col fade-up">
            <h3>Mission</h3>
            <p>
              A Million Women Africa exists to mobilize women and men as
              modern-day Esthers and Mordecais—awakening nations to prayer,
              fasting, and spiritual transformation through monthly prayer and
              training, annual gatherings centered around the Day of Atonement,
